ActNational Aboriginal Economic Development Board Order
PrecisReappointment of DAWN MADAHBEE of Little Current, Ontario, as a member of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years; and designation of DAWN MADAHBEE as Vice-Chairperson of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board.
